{"tid":1826871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［金系魔法師召喚」除左繼續課金比立場同蘋果，你仲可以......","createTime":"2020-01-16T13:05:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T11:53:45.000Z","uid":30138,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4a0726b5a767c3a1a85480ce44123a24634e783a","tid":1826871,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T13:05:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">課埋比獨媒同傳真社！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n佢地冇咁多人睇，但亦都相對佢地係冇咁多資源、人力、物力。<br />\n<br />\n但咁絕對唔代表佢地冇心！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n相反，雖然獨媒同傳真冇咁商業，但佢地既報導仍然好撚深入。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如係依場運動之前，獨媒已經一直有跟緊本地足球同各區區議會；依場運動佢地都馬不停蹄咁不斷做LIVE，你睇返佢FB或者係現場見到就知，獨媒弟弟沙田又去，屯門又去，coverage多過Kante、妹妹又係，後生女仔老是長出現。大行動又報、細行動更加報，雖然高登年代不時有人屌佢地左膠，但講行動力講專業，真係無出其右。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重點係，佢地team得好撚少人，都可以run到咁，唔課唔得la下話。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">獨媒社區報眾籌計劃</span></span>：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/36XtZQi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F36XtZQi&d=LzGu2J%2BtBqWvyoHzd7Q7GDQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=917b5b4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/36XtZQi</a><br />\n<br />\n有睇就知，同一般媒體相比，傳真比較主要做多D深入報導。例如之前既831調查、更耐之前既三跑、明日大嶼跟進......每樣野都係好撚重要而又深入；佢地仲要做埋英文版，國際文宣，又係好值得支持！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">傳真社月捐</span></span>：<a href=\"https://www.factwire.org/backus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.factwire.org%2Fbackus&d=LzGu2J%2BtBqWvyoHzd7Q7GDQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=e05f9fa8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.factwire.org/backus</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">抵制紅媒、由我做起</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">月捐夠雷、力撐黃媒</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/04/29/S1l94b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F04%2F29%2FS1l94b.jpg&h=a8cc691f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e21f49df5060be60419516d8ea7e28af611276b","tid":1826871,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T13:07:05.000Z","msg":"西九拍照被捕青年被扣足48 小時  保釋金高達<span style=\"color: red;\">七千元</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1826845\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1826845</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ovxufob.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvxufob.jpg&h=385cc0b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b801db41786913fba980398a2f5ae3b501b87c7b","tid":1826871,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T13:07:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">入錢入錢入錢</span></span>"},{"pid":"1fcb10ffb5c3f3660357ab6354934a8406cfbe07","tid":1826871,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T13:08:04.000Z","msg":"我反對你的反對啊！屌你老母<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1826837\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1826837</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2d07abaf03e31488c537e27d5369bd071a2ffb88","tid":1826871,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T13:08:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">（新方向）文宣用作包裝銷售</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1826045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1826045</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3a25b7d77e0f13b74017d17b835ab5e3945aff9d","tid":1826871,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T13:10:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">入錢入錢入錢</span></span>"},{"pid":"2c8e08d